   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sl097a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Spring Hill Maury <choice>
                           <abbr>Co. Tenn.</abbr>
                           <expan>County Tennessee</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <date when="1847-12-03">3rd December 1847</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Dear Sir:</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I have on hand some twenty pieces of rope &amp; bagging each, a new &amp; good articles from the factory of <name type="person">Mr <choice>
                     <abbr>Jas</abbr>
                     <expan>James</expan>
                  </choice> Lugh</name> of <name type="place">Williamson</name>.</p>
            <p>As you are well acquainted with the quality, and learning that you were recently in want, I write to inform you that I will sell the lot at 5 per cent less than the current market price.</p>
            <p>You will please inform me, on the receipt of this, whether you will take it.</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>Very Respectfully <choice>
                     <abbr>&amp;c</abbr>
                     <expan>et cetera</expan>
                  </choice>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Gen.</abbr>
                        <expan>General</expan>
                     </choice> W. White</name>
               </signed>
               <pb n="2" facs="sl097b.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>Spring Hill <choice>
                        <abbr>T.</abbr>
                        <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <date when="1847-12-03">
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>Dec</abbr>
                           <expan>December</expan>
                        </choice> 3rd</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <add place="above address">Paid 5</add>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="person">Mr <choice>
                           <abbr>Thos.</abbr>
                           <expan>Thomas</expan>
                        </choice> Abernathy</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Elkton</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Giles County</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">{<choice>
                           <abbr>Tenne</abbr>
                           <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
